string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_FANATIC_Gossip_02
string.body: You'll drown in blood. Do you hear me? In blood!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_GateKeeper_Satk_01
string.body: My Flaying Curse will tear apart your soul!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimBoss_Batk_01
string.body: Who dares seek out the Petralith?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimBoss_Satk_01
string.body: You're stronger than I thought, but not strong enough.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimBoss_Satk_02
string.body: Hah! Your puny arms will be your undoing.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimBoss_Satk_03
string.body: This rock shall be your grave.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimBoss_Satk_06
string.body: I'll bury you under the ground you walk on.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimBoss_Satk_07
string.body: Now you've done it. No mercy!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimBoss_Die_01
string.body: Great Aion! Please forgive your poor servant...who has failed to fulfill his duties...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimExpert_Batk_01
string.body: I'll kill anyone who disturbs my work!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimExpert_Satk_01
string.body: You, weaver. Get over here and help me.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimExpert_Satk_02
string.body: May the undying flame burn you to ashes!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_NepilimExpert_Satk_03
string.body: I'll beat you to a paste!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_FANATIC_Idle_Gossip_03
string.body: I think this is a sign of Daevas...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_FANATIC_Idle_Gossip_05
string.body: I've got a bad feeling about this.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_FANATIC_Idle_Gossip_08
string.body: It's been a long time since I went out...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTP_FANATIC_Idle_Gossip_10
string.body: Did you catch what Lord Malika said a second ago?

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Shulack_Knight_Gossip_01
string.body: I can forgive Krall mocking, but...

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Shulack_Knight_Gossip_02
string.body: I can't forgive those who mock Krall!

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Shulack_Gossip_01
string.body: You'll never get back home alive!

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_ArchPriest2_Gossip_01
string.body: You pitiful worms! Kneel before your betters.

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_ArchPriest2_Gossip_02
string.body: Do you think the Seal of Tiamat is nothing?

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_ArchPriest2_Gossip_03
string.body: This is the end. Your end.

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_DeathKnight_Gossip_04
string.body: You thought I'd make an easy target?

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Shulack_Rufukin
string.body: You saved my life. Thank you very much!

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_DeathKnight_Taros
string.body: Finally! I'm free of the curse! I'll never forget your kindness.

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Spectre_Ahbahna
string.body: I curse you all. From the depths of the Abyss, a curse upon all who disturb the graves!

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Taros_EnterAttackState
string.body: Tiamat's servants, rejoice! I've come for you.

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Archpriest_Gossip_02
string.body: You'll always be a slave, Taros!

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Archpriest_DeadlyAttack
string.body: By the glory of the Great Dragon Lord, the wing of death shall spread across the world!

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Archpriest_Gossip_03
string.body: Do you have any idea what a mistake you've made?

string.name: STR_IDCatacombs_Boss_Archpriest_LeaveAttackState
string.body: Fools! Now do you understand the might of the Balaur?

string.name: STR_LF4_Gateway_Li_Guard_Boss_AL_Gossip_02
string.body: Focus! The enemy will fall before us!

string.name: STR_DF4_Gateway_Da_Guard_Boss_AL_Gossip_03
string.body: Do you really think I'll give up?

string.name: STR_DF4_Owllaunamed_Ah_Gossip_01
string.body: You managed to get this far?

string.name: STR_DF4_OwllauPriest_Ae_Gossip_01
string.body: It is too late for regrets!

string.name: STR_IDCT_Boss_StatueDrakan_system_01
string.body: Virhana's Curse activates once the Indomitable Armor disappears.

string.name: STR_IDCT_Boss_StatueDrakan_01
string.body: Who dares despoil this holy place?

string.name: STR_IDCT_Boss_StatueDrakan_02
string.body: My curse shall be upon you!

string.name: STR_IDCT_TiamatDrakan_01_Batk_b
string.body: Bow to Lord Tiamat's will, or face the consequences.

string.name: STR_IDCT_Boss_LichKing_03
string.body: That'll make a meal for Master Macunbello!

string.name: STR_IDCT_Boss_Rudra_01
string.body: Freedom! And what luck that you're the first thing I've seen, Daeva.

string.name: STR_IDCT_Boss_Rudra_03
string.body: Come, thunder. Come, lightning. Wreak your havoc!

string.name: STR_IDCT_Boss_Rudra_05
string.body: I can feel it. My powers are coming back!

string.name: STR_IDCT_Boss_Rudra_06
string.body: Even sealed, you worthless bugs are no match for me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Q20023_FanaticWiQ_52_An_001_Batk_S
string.body: Hello, airon. Come for the slaughter?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Q20023_FanaticWiQ_52_An_002_atk_S
string.body: I won't hurt you too much.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Q20023_FanaticWiQ_53_An_001_Batk_S
string.body: You'll beg to serve Lord Beritra!

string.name: STR_LF4_Raidnew_Gossip_01
string.body: The intruders shall be judged! -before Showtime (Temporary)

string.name: STR_LF4_RaidnewsumA_Gossip_02
string.body: I will self-destruct before you take me! (Temporary)

string.name: STR_LF4_RaidnewsumB_Gossip_01
string.body: Nothing but pain for the intruders! (Temporary)

string.name: STR_LF4_RaidnewsumE_Gossip_02
string.body: Don't miss your chance to die! (Temporary)

string.name: STR_DF4_Raidnew_Gossip_04
string.body: It's too late for regrets!-before Showtime (Temporary)

string.name: STR_Dread02_Drakan_Boss_01
string.body: Thou shalt all return to the Aether's flow!

string.name: STR_Dread02_Drakan_Boss_02
string.body: Kneel before the might of the earth!

string.name: STR_Dread02_Drakan_Boss_04
string.body: I will not be undone by some lowly Daevas!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDNovice_02_DBrownieWWa_named_18_an_1_Die_S
string.body: Where am I? Why is Kobold here...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDNovice_05_RatmanMWa_named_19_an_1_Die_S
string.body: Odella to Master Hamerun... Hamerun? Who is Hamerun, MuMu...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanAs_55_Ae_kcsat4_b
string.body: Thou shalt regret sullying this place!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanAsNoble_55_Ae_kcast4_b
string.body: Canst thee not see the wings of death hovering over thee?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanAsNoble_55_Ae_kcast8_b
string.body: Kneel before the power of Lord Tiamat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanFiNoble_55_Ae_kcast4_b
string.body: I'll show thee the true power of the Chantra Legion!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanFiNoble_55_Ae_kcast8_b
string.body: How dost it feel to come face to face with thy own Vanishment?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanScNoble_55_Ae_kcast2_b
string.body: This arrow will be the messenger of death!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanScNoble_55_Ae_kcast3_b
string.body: How dare ye set foot in here! Pay for thy insolence with Vanishment!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanWiNoble_55_Ae_kcast3_b
string.body: I will show thee the epic darkness of Vanishment!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanWiNoble_55_Ae_kcast5_b
string.body: Thou shalt come to learn the greatness of Lord Tiamat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanClNoble_55_Ae_kcast8_b
string.body: For the glory of the Chantra Legion!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanWiBonus_55_Ae_001_Batk_b
string.body: How could they let these ignorant Daevas come this far?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanWiBonus_55_Ae_kcast4_b
string.body: Behold the incredible might of Kamanya!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_DrakanAsWait_55_Ae_kcast4_b
string.body: You won't get to lay a finger on these supplies!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDNovice_02_DBrownieWWo_18_an_1_Idle_S
string.body: I won't lose the Odium! It will go to the Haramel Tower!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDNovice_05_RatmanGathererMWa_19_an_1_Idle_S
string.body: I haven't dug the Odella to send to the tower... You are interrupting me, MuMu!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDNovice_07_DBrownieWWa_keeper_20_an_1_Idle_S
string.body: We will need another iron cage!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDNovice_04_RatmanMWa_Key_18_an_1_Idle_S
string.body: I won't give the key to you, MuMu.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Underpass_NepilimNamed_55_Al_001_idle_S
string.body: Aaaargh, I will not forgive you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Underpass_NepilimNamed_55_Al_002_idle_S
string.body: I can't bear this any longer!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_PrisonerWoman3_38_An_001_Idle_S
string.body: Hehehe, I'm going to kill you all.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_PrisonerMan4_38_An_001_Idle_S
string.body: Think you can get out of here alive...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_Rguard2_38_An_001_Idle_S
string.body: Ahhh, how refreshing! This is why I do this work.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_Rguard2_38_An_002_Idle_S
string.body: Hey! Give us something to eat here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_PrisonGuards_38_An_1_Batk_S
string.body: How convenient, you spare me the trouble of looking for you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_Trigger_Torture_38_An_001_Idle_S
string.body: Heh heh.... You won't be able to resist for much longer.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Mguard5_38_An_001_Idle_S
string.body: I wonder when I can see his Honor, the judge...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Mguard5_38_An_002_Idle_S
string.body: It's getting harder and harder to make a living.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Rguard5_38_An_001_Idle_S
string.body: I don't know if she will like it or not.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Rguard5_38_An_002_Idle_S
string.body: I couldn't tell you the last time I saw some Kinah...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Chef2_38_An_001_Idle_S
string.body: I prepared a special dish today, so everyone please try it.

string.name: STR_IDCromede_1low_Hierarch
string.body: I will send you away painlessly!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4_DrakanEvent_01
string.body: I will kill you all, you pathetic Elyos!

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdA_EnterAttackState
string.body: Curses to those who disturb the Current of Life.

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdA_UseSkill
string.body: O Breath of Life, return to the embrace of Pazuzu!

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdA_OnDie_01
string.body: Finally... I can return to him...

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdA_OnDie_02
string.body: Pazuzu has finally... found a way to return...

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdD_EnterAttackState_02
string.body: Your pathetic power won't get you to the artifact.

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdD_UseSkill_01
string.body: You dare threaten me with attacks such as that!

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdD_UseSkill_02
string.body: Creatures of Aether, come forth and aid me!

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdD_UseSkill_03
string.body: Return to the flow of Aether, Daevas!

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdD_UseSkill_04
string.body: Only death awaits those who intrude.

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdD_OnDie
string.body: Ah... I must protect... the... Tower...

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdDH_EnterAttackState_01
string.body: You won't touch the artifact, no matter what happens!

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdDH_EnterAttackState_02
string.body: Those who threaten the artifact shall be returned to the flow of Aether!

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdDH_UseSkill_01
string.body: Face the wrath of the protector!

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdDH_UseSkill_02
string.body: Only death awaits those who intrude.

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdDH_OnDie_01
string.body: I will curse you until the end...

string.name: STR_IDAbRe_Core_NmdDH_OnDie_02
string.body: Ah... The power, the power of... Aion is...

string.name: STR_CHAT_BIDNovice_BrownieWa_NM_20_An_1_kcast1_b
string.body: Save me! Save me! Save me! Waaah!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4Raid_02
string.body: Omega summons a creature. Rise from your slumber, my golem!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4Raid_03
string.body: Omega and his summoned creature use a condition changing skill on the player. Power of the ancient dragon!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4Raid_04
string.body: Omega and his summoned creature begin their attack. Go, my faithful golem!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4Raid_05
string.body: Omega summons a creature that gives him great strength. Rise from your slumber, my brother!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF4Raid_01
string.body: Ha ha ha, I will destroy everything! (Balaurean)

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF4Raid_05
string.body: I curse this world that created me! (Strong Balaurean)

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_01
string.body: Time to show you my hidden powers!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_02
string.body: Turn back now and I might forgive you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_03
string.body: I can't let the seal be broken like this....

string.name: STR_CHAT_BIDCromede_2low_Key_GuardBoss_38_An_1_Batk_S
string.body: You have some guts coming out of there!

string.name: STR_CHAT_BGuardBoss_02
string.body: Damn it, master Kaliga has raised a Karnif pup.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BIDCromede_2low_Key_GuardBoss_38_An_1_Die_S
string.body: Nevertheless, you won't be able to leave here alive!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Torture_01
string.body: Kukuku, what do we have here...a new toy?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Torture_02
string.body: What do you think of this pain?

string.name: STR_CHAT_BIDCromede_2up_Key_Butler_38_An_1_Die_S
string.body: I must inform my master that a guest has arrived....

string.name: STR_CHAT_Wife_01
string.body: Oh my! Who are you, and how dare you stroll into my bedroom just like that?!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Wife_02
string.body: Why don't you try playing with my kids?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Wife_03
string.body: Just wait. Once I let my husband know, you will be finished.

string.name: STR_CHAT_AssiJudge_01
string.body: My skills are superior to yours!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Trigger_Wound_Wife_38_An_1_Batk_S
string.body: My husband is angry now! You are finished!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Trigger_Wound_AssiJudge_38_An_1_Batk_S
string.body: It's time for payback...you better be prepared!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Trigger_Wound_Torture_38_An_1_Batk_S
string.body: I will let you feel my fury once more.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Judge_01
string.body: What...what are you all doing? Attack! Attack!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Judge_03
string.body: Still, you shouldn't look down on me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Judge_04
string.body: I seem to have raised a...Karnif pup!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AngryJudge_01
string.body: You dare challenge me? How exciting!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AngryJudge_03
string.body: Beg for my forgiveness, before it's too late!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AngryJudge_04
string.body: You really...fan the flame of my anger.

string.name: STR_CHAT_AngryJudge_05
string.body: To think that I'd ever be forced onto my knees....

string.name: STR_CHAT_BIDNovice_RatmanWa_NM_20_An_1_katk2_b
string.body: MuMu Ham is dead! Ugh! Stop hitting me! MuMu!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_04
string.body: Shhh. First give a prayer to Empyrean Lady Siel.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_05
string.body: I see that mere words aren't going to be enough.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_06
string.body: Lady Siel, please save the one who has been a fool.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_07
string.body: I shall easily send you away!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_08
string.body: I guess I have no choice but to resort to this.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Hierarch_11
string.body: And give enlightenment to the foolish one!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Judge_05
string.body: No dinner for those who have been lazy!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Judge_06
string.body: This is precisely what those who seek to better themselves need!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Judge_07
string.body: You have become powerful, Kromede. But still not enough to contend with me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Judge_08
string.body: I feel tired and need some rest.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Judge_10
string.body: You still have a long way to go. I will summon an opponent who will suit you perfectly.

string.name: STR_CHAT_AngryJudge_09
string.body: Beg for forgiveness before it's too late!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AngryJudge_10
string.body: You fool, it's too late for regrets!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_ServantMan_38_An_1_Batk_S
string.body: I shall beat some sense into you with my broom.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_ServantWoman_38_An_1_Batk_S
string.body: And I just finished cleaning, too. I can't forgive you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Mguard2_38_An_2_Batk_S
string.body: You traitor! How dare you show up here like this!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Mguard4_38_An_2_Batk_S
string.body: This is no place for you to be, Kromede!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Rguard2_38_An_1_Batk_S
string.body: We have intruders inside the manor!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Rguard2_38_An_2_Batk_S
string.body: How did you manage to make it this far?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2up_Rguard4_38_An_2_Batk_S
string.body: Intruders! Check for any weak points in the security!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_Chef_Event_03
string.body: Will you be able to cook up anything decent that way?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_Chef_Event_04
string.body: I will do my best, head chef!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDCromede_2low_PrisonerWoman3_38_An_002_Idle_S
string.body: It is so damn tiring being surrounded by so many ugly beings!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Maravata01
string.body: Problematic elements identified. Initiating elimination procedures.

string.name: STR_CHAT_ShulackNM_07
string.body: Eliminating all life forms within range.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Branch_Event_Shulackwizard_99_n_1_Batk_S
string.body: Actually I'm a salt thief!! Puhaha!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Branch_Event_XmasEvent_Rudolph_99_n_1_Batk_S
string.body: Hey, I was just taking a break, nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Branch_Event_XmasEvent_Rudolph_99_n_2_Batk_S
string.body: This will not get you any presents, naughty Daeva!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Branch_Event_XmasEvent_ShugoSantaD_99_n_1_Batk_S
string.body: Stop it! My union will hear about this, nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Branch_Event_XmasEvent_ShugoSantaD_99_n_2_Batk_S
string.body: Fine, fine, I am going! Just leave me alone!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Drana_Shulack_01
string.body: You saved my life. Thank you very much!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Drana_Shulack_02
string.body: Go to Inokin! He will repay you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Drana_Named_B_02
string.body: I will send the cursed ones to the flow of Aether!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Drana_Named_B_03
string.body: Ugh, Warden Surama, I've failed you...

string.name: STR_CHAT_Drana_Named_E_02
string.body: You dare to ruin my experiment?!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Drana_Named_E_03
string.body: Flap your wings, little Daeva, but you'll never escape!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Drana_Named_E_05
string.body: How could my plans... be ruined like this...?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuFIKN_01
string.body: We won't let Daevas steal our technology!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuWIPR_01
string.body: This Balaur technology is ours! Bought and paid for!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuRAAS_01
string.body: We won't let you escape with our secrets!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuFIKN_02
string.body: No Daevas will get away with our technology!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuWIPR_02
string.body: We'll destroy the power generator before we let Daevas get their hands on it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuRAAS_02
string.body: No! We worked so hard to get that technology!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuGuardian_01
string.body: We have intruders! Alert the elder!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuGuardian_02
string.body: Don't you dare touch the power generator!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuGuardian_03
string.body: Only Engineering League members past this point.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuGuardian_04
string.body: No Daevas in here, I'm warning you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_ShuGuardian_05
string.body: Now that you've come inside, you won't get out unscathed!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_DrakanWI_01
string.body: No Daeva will touch Master Ashunatal!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_DrakanGuardian_01
string.body: What were the Watchers thinking to allow Daevas to get this far?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_DrakanWiNoble_01
string.body: Destroy them! Don't let them disturb Master Ashunatal!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDStation_Zone3Boss_01
string.body: Impressive. But this is as far as you go!

string.name: STR_CHAT_S2_Saam1_02
string.body: Tsk, so you know what's good for your health, eh!

string.name: STR_CHAT_S3_Elemeltal_Water_55_Ah
string.body: My tides will make you dance!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S6_VanqJr_55_An
string.body: You sealed me! I've killed Daevas before, youngling, and I'll kill them again. Starting with you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_B1_Arminos1s

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_B1_Arminos2s1

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_B1_Arminos2s2

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_B1_Arminos3s2

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_B1_ArminosFs1

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_B1_ArminosFs2

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4_System3

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4_Komu3
string.body: My mane is something else, huh?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S1_Agrint

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4B_Bbobi

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Hameroon_Die

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Kaliga
string.body: I will destroy anyone who stands in my way!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Fi_L
string.body: Relax... This will be over soon....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Ma_L
string.body: I'll go easy on you. There's no sport in obliteration.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Pr_L_Die
string.body: Next time... I won't go so easy!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Kaliga_Orb
string.body: Time to use the Crystal Ball.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Fi_Change
string.body: See how you do against Templar skills...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4_Wir_01
string.body: Know your place, cur! Your skills are inadequate!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4_Anger_01
string.body: Where are the guards! Who are you?!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4_Anger_02
string.body: My beautiful Bloodwings will see to you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4_Hammam_01
string.body: Your body can only take so many blows, pup.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4_Hammam_02
string.body: Haha! Maybe I should try some of my torture methods...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S4_Hammam_03
string.body: Ugh. How could I be worse... Than you?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Enchant_02
string.body: At least the godstone won't go to waste with you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Trade_01
string.body: I brought my favorite weapon. Let's fight! Nyerk nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Trade_02
string.body: Strong Daeva! Knew it! Saw it in your eyes! Yes yes!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_As_D
string.body: My weapon's broken and rotting. You shouldn't be afraid to fight!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_As_D_Die
string.body: Yes, yes. You should be able to do this much, at least.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Ma_D
string.body: Don't just stand there - attack me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Pr_D_Die
string.body: May the Empyrean Lords... Watch over you...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Pr_Change_D
string.body: Grant this Cleric power, Lord Marchutan!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Enchant_01_D
string.body: Have you socketed a godstone yet?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Enchant_02_D
string.body: Yes! The godstone will not be wasted in your hands.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Trade_01_D
string.body: You don't underestimate a trade broker!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_Solo_S5_Ware_01_D
string.body: I'm as good a fighter as I am a warehouse manager! Fight me!

string.body: Daevas? Thou art fools to come here!

string.body: I'll make a wandering Raksang ghost!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDRaksha_DrakanKnight_Ae_Attack_HitPoint
string.body: Come. I'll show you true horror!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDRaksha_DrakanBoneKnight_Ae_Attack_HitPoint

string.body: Thy presence is unwelcome, filthy Daeva!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_DrakanVil_02
string.body: The Terath Legion is no common foe!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_DrakanNoble_01
string.body: Die for the honor of Lord Tiamat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_DrakanNoble_02
string.body: Embrace the futility of thy cause!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_DrakanF_01
string.body: This Dredgion shall deliver thee to thy doom!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Hack_01
string.body: Defend the Surkana at all costs!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Hack_02
string.body: Thou shalt not touch this Surkana!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Control
string.body: Thou shalt regret stepping into my domain!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Supply_01
string.body: Mayhap thy flesh shalt make fine rations!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Supply_02
string.body: This is no place for the likes of thee!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Wait_01
string.body: Thy impudence shall be rewarded with death!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Wait_02
string.body: The Drakan rule over you filth!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Giant_01
string.body: Ah, finally, a balm to this dull duty!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Named_Giant_02
string.body: Thy weakness is evident to all with eyes.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_SemiBoss
string.body: Didst thou actually think the Captain would be undefended?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Boss
string.body: Thou hast caused much grief on my ship. Now it is time to pay!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_03_Gravity
string.body: This room shall be thy grave!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDArena_MC_End2

string.name: STR_CHAT_ValentineEvent_Brownie_Solo_01
string.body: Welcome, freedom! Banish the ties that bind.

string.name: STR_CHAT_ValentineEvent_Brownie_Solo_02
string.body: Do you know how expensive dating can be?

string.name: STR_CHAT_ValentineEvent_Brownie_Solo_03

string.name: STR_CHAT_ValentineEvent_Shulack_Couple_01

string.name: STR_CHAT_ValentineEvent_Shulack_Couple_02
string.body: My sweetheart is so much stronger and better than you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_As_Broad_01
string.body: You lazy bums! Move your rumps and help!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_As_Broad_02
string.body: Group together unless you want to die!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_As_Broad_03
string.body: Let me show you what our combined power can do!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_As_Broad_04

string.body: Now we're elite? Even Kobolds laugh at us.

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_Broad_04
string.body: Nobody is feeling good, so why us?

string.body: I may look defeated, but I can still kill you…

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_2_Die_b
string.body: This might be the end for me. How disappointing...

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_SemiNamed_1_Batk_b
